{
  "stem": "7358.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a great reunion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And before they took me into the house, they stripped me of all my clothes, and they burned it outside, and they had clean clothes for me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They bathed me and everything else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I got so excited that I asked them to put the electric on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I forgot there was no electric, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "People used to-- you were lucky if you had a little kerosene.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Most of the farmers used to use wood which was saturated with some kind of substance that burns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they used to use that wood to light in a corner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was just very, very-- even the farmers had-- certain things were just not available.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And during the night, when I woke up in the morning, the smell of my feet was just-- my feet were able to thaw.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were frozen over time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So it was a nice warm house, and everything became normal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my feet were in terrible condition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And again, my uncle, because he had the weapons, and he was a doer, a fighter, he went, and he forced the doctor, a Christian doctor, to come.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I don't-- I'm not sure if he was Polish or Ukrainian, from some village.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he came to examine my feet, and he said that there was-- no, he didn't come.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He gave advice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He said we should look for pig fat and bandage my legs with the fat of a pig.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And perhaps that's the only thing that he can suggest to do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they did it for a day or two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, my toes were just hanging in the skin of the foot.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
